[42.580526, "o", "Here are the services exposed in the default namespace:                                                                                                                                 \r\n\r\n\u001b[1m • \u001b[0m\u001b[1mkubernetes\u001b[0m: Type ClusterIP, Cluster IP 10.96.0.1, No external IP, Port 443/TCP, Age 19 hours.                                                                                        \r\n\u001b[1m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1m • \u001b[0mThis is the default Kubernetes service that provides API access to the cluster.                                                                                                   \r\n\u001b[1m • \u001b[0m\u001b[1mnginx\u001b[0m: Type ClusterIP, Cluster IP 10.96.212.3, No external IP, Port 80/TCP, Age 15 hours.                                                                                            \r\n\u001b[1m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1m • \u001b[0mThis service exposes an Nginx deployment internally within the cluster.                                                                                                           \r\n\r\n\u001b[1;35mConclusion\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                              \r\n\r\nThe services are correctly set up and running within the default namespace. If you need to expose these services externally, consider using a \u001b[1;36;40mLoadBalancer\u001b[0m or \u001b[1;36;40mNodePort\u001b[0m type for the     \r\n\u001b[1;36;40mnginx\u001b[0m service.                                                                                                                                                                          \r\n"]
[42.64268, "o", "\u001b[?2004h\u001b]0;zangetzu@GhostShell: ~/projects/infra-copilot\u0007\u001b[01;32mzangetzu@GhostShell\u001b[00m:\u001b[01;34m~/projects/infra-copilot\u001b[00m$ "]
[45.89512, "o", "\u001b[7muv run copilot ask \"how many restarts have the pods had?\"\u001b[27m"]
